{"tid":1821380,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中東局勢惡化，淡友又有希望？","createTime":"2020-01-12T08:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T02:06:03.000Z","uid":316667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fe535bc9167101f9b7ed526b992e5906dca309","tid":1821380,"uid":316667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"伊拉克人民動員組織指揮官遭暗殺<br />\n當地時間1月12日，伊拉克人民動員委員會證實，人民動員組織的&ldquo;卡爾巴拉旅&rdquo;指揮官薩阿迪在巴格達遭暗殺。事件發生在11日晚間，當時薩阿迪身處巴格達北部的薩德爾城，有兩名護衞隨行，遭到不明槍手襲擊身亡。薩阿迪在人民動員組織中的地位較高，此次暗殺事件的動機目前尚不明朗。"},{"pid":"a48344e6c603c7b8a9e4e5a5ba51a6e185d6dd2d","tid":1821380,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"11180fc5382cbbea8a9f789b90d579af029d0e13","tid":1821380,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:50:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e3b150d52042a3b1486b731b58cad651cd1c8bd","tid":1821380,"uid":198536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"利淡消息都係升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69716b52264662ab8e745aea3d60007c1af7c16","tid":1821380,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"255ca1ac2ecd0b52f349a178ebcdd32374cf6ab8","tid":1821380,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"第日咪又即刻升返再破頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f9d82943cfa17b8e79d175597892c5741626fe","tid":1821380,"uid":252069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"屌你! 黃色經濟圈根本影響唔到d資源分配!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無所謂<br />\n因為學波蘭人將抗爭融入生活先係目的</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">明明好成功,我哋錯咗重點啫,調整心態就得</span><br />\n- 分享自 L